OL,5, Firms exposed by Michael Gove for      
OL,6, failing to sign a contract to repair   
OL,7, post-Grenfell safety risks have joined 
OL,8, the scheme.                            
OL,10,FThe housing secretary gave companies   
OL,11,Funtil 13 March to sign the agreement   
OL,12,Faimed at addressing cladding issues    
OL,13,Fexposed by the Grenfell Tower fire.    
OL,15,FMr Gove named the 11 firms that failed 
OL,16,Fto sign the contract, which would see  
OL,17,Fthem spending #2bn to pay for repairs. 
OL,19,FOn Friday, the government revealed five
OL,20,Fof these had now joined the scheme.    
